WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.000
Teenager sells her old bath water in bottles

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:11.000
A woman in England is selling her bath water.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:15.000
It is so popular that the water has sold out.

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:20.000
The woman is Instagram cosplay model Belle Delphine.

00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:26.000
She has over four million followers across the social media site.

00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:34.000
She posted a video to her Instagram page advertising small jars of her old bath water for $30.

00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:42.000
In the video, she said: "Gamer boys - It's time to get your gamer girl bath water."

00:00:43.000 --> 00:00:50.000
She added: "This water is not for drinking and should only be used for sentimental purposes."

00:00:51.000 --> 00:00:57.000
She then winks at the camera and lets water from her mouth drip into a small bottle.

00:00:58.000 --> 00:01:02.000
Thousands of her fans eagerly placed an order for the water.

00:01:02.500 --> 00:01:08.000
Her entire stock of 500 jars of the water sold out within two days.

00:01:09.000 --> 00:01:12.000
Belle Delphine is a 19-year-old Londoner.

00:01:13.000 --> 00:01:21.000
She has gained a lot of popularity on social media by sitting in a bath filled with water in skimpy clothes.

00:01:22.000 --> 00:01:24.000
She also calls herself Gamer Girl.

00:01:25.000 --> 00:01:31.000
Selling her old bath water is her latest idea to make money from her followers.

00:01:32.000 --> 00:01:37.000
Another way she makes money is by selling selfies of herself.

00:01:38.000 --> 00:01:43.000
Followers can pay up to $2,500 for some of the selfies.

00:01:44.000 --> 00:01:49.000
Belle said she is constantly trying to "come up with weird ideas" to make money.

00:01:50.000 --> 00:01:56.000
Her bath water idea has not been popular with everyone on social media.

00:01:56.500 --> 00:01:59.000
Many people said it was "gross".

00:02:00.000 --> 00:02:06.000
An Instagram user commented: "Every day, we stray further and further away from God."

00:02:07.000 --> 00:02:16.000
Other people praised her business skills.
